{"tid":2159626,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"點滴：抱1歲子投票 教育民主","createTime":"2020-08-16T12:17:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T12:21:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0bfe854b2b2089fdb3b803891f687598e4d13bf5","tid":2159626,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T12:17:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200816/5BGOYO2WMFD73MUKMAUABVQNI4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200816%2F5BGOYO2WMFD73MUKMAUABVQNI4%2F&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJPpmn865KX7g3oX29oYbiiE%3D&h=fac3e4ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200816%2F5BGOYO2WMFD73MUKMAUABVQNI4%2F&h=24739745\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200816/5BGOYO2WMFD73MUKMAUABVQNI4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n點滴：抱1歲子投票 教育民主<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/MGoErBhij7qmMDjxbJ-xUfvWwPY=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HAOECFE7KZEOFLWQL3P7X7DXHQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMGoErBhij7qmMDjxbJ-xUfvWwPY%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHAOECFE7KZEOFLWQL3P7X7DXHQ.jpg&h=3e9bf1a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓國瑜<br />\n<br />\n台灣立法院三讀通過修正選罷法部份條文，允許6歲以下兒童進入投票所，民進黨立委趙天麟昨抱着1歲多的兒子進入票站投票，他表示這是民主教育的一環。趙在苓雅國中投票，全家總動員，媽媽、太太及兒女一同前往，他一手抱着小兒子、一手投選票，格外受關注。他指出，上次罷韓投票雖然已適用新法，但小兒子因沒有口罩不能進入，這次為兒子備好口罩，就是要抱着孩子進去投票，「讓大家了解這是機會教育、民主教育的一環」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點滴：韓教懷孕秘訣 吃百鵝蛋<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。台灣名醫、茂盛生殖醫學中心院長李茂盛向媒體表示，這種偏方自己聽都沒聽過，也沒有科學證據，更指鵝蛋的蛋黃含有很多膽固醇，吃多了只會造成心血管疾病。"},{"pid":"5a971501599c341d93926d6982ab4420da93c4e4","tid":2159626,"uid":363651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T12:21:29.000Z","msg":"乜真係會有膽固醇咩？"}]}